OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784099887
OL,3,CSome residents allowed to return to
OL,4,Ccaravan park after major fire
OL,6,FSome residents are being allowed to
OL,7,Freturn home to a Oxfordshire caravan
OL,8,Fpark which was engulfed by a major
OL,9,Ffire over the weekend.
OL,11,FThames Valley Police said only those
OL,12,Fliving in parts of Oaks caravan park
OL,13,F"where it is deemed there is no risk"
OL,14,Fare permitted to do so.
OL,16,FMore than 125 firefighters tackled the
OL,17,Fblaze in Fyfield Wick, near Kingston
OL,18,FBagpuize, on Sunday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
