OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784099887
OL,3,CSome residents allowed to return to
OL,4,Ccaravan park after major fire
OL,6,FThe cause of the fire, which also
OL,7,Fspread to surrounding fields, is
OL,8,Fcurrently considered as accidental.
OL,10,FThe force added that a number of
OL,11,Froads, which were temporarily closed,
OL,12,Fhave now re-opened.
OL,14,FThey include closures on Faringdon
OL,15,FRoad, the A415 Kingston Road, A338 and
OL,16,FDigging Lane.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
