CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784099887
OL,3,CSome residents allowed to return to
OL,4,Ccaravan park after major fire
OL,6,FThe alarm was raised on Sunday
OL,7,Fafternoon, with 14 fire crews, seven
OL,8,Fspecialist vehicles and additional
OL,9,Fofficers from across Oxfordshire in
OL,10,Fattendance at the height of the fire.
OL,12,FThey were supported by assets from
OL,13,FDorset and Wiltshire Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService, Royal Berkshire Fire and
OL,15,FRescue Service and Buckinghamshire
OL,16,FFire & Rescue Service.
OL,18,FPlumes of smoke could be seen for
OL,19,Fmiles, with those that had to leave
OL,20,Ftheir homes taken to a nearby sports
OL,21,Fground.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
