OL,3,CSome residents allowed to return to
OL,4,Ccaravan park after major fire
OL,6,FThey are being supported by Thames
OL,7,FValley Police, Oxfordshire County
OL,8,FCouncil's Joint Oxfordshire Resilience
OL,9,FTeam, Rapid Relief Team UK, South &
OL,10,FVale district council and other local
OL,11,Forganisations.
